/**
 * Privent wire contracts — v1.
 *
 * Single source of truth for SDK <-> Backend <-> ML DTOs. Backend
 * (class-validator) and ML (pydantic) DTOs are derived manually; parity is
 * enforced by `__tests__/contracts.parity.test.ts`.
 *
 * Versioning rules (master plan §5.3):
 * - Field additions are additive-only within v1 (request: optional + default;
 *   response: nullable, eski alan korunur).
 * - Removals require a deprecation window then a major bump (`/v2/`).
 * - Open string unions (EntityKind, AuditEventV1.type) tolerate runtime
 *   extension; closed enums (RiskLevel, EntitySource) require a major bump.
 */
